---
const contactSectionUrl = "#contato";
---

<section
  class="ateb-grid-pattern relative overflow-hidden pb-16 pt-[clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem)] md:pb-24"
  id="hero"
>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_12%_22%,rgba(179,209,51,0.18),transparent_24%),radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_30%,rgba(179,209,51,0.14),transparent_22%),radial-gradient(circle_at_86%_72%,rgba(77,72,55,0.08),transparent_20%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="ateb-container relative">
    <div
      class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:min-h-[calc(100vh-10rem)] lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:gap-14"
    >
      <div class="grid gap-6 text-center lg:text-left">
        <h1
          class="font-sora mx-auto max-w-[18ch] text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-[1.06] tracking-[-0.06em] text-ateb-dark lg:mx-0"
        >
          Consultoria em ERP

          <span
            class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 lg:justify-start"
          >
            <img
              src="/Logo/TOTVS.webp"
              alt="TOTVS"
              class="h-12 w-auto object-contain brightness-0 md:h-14 lg:h-16"
            />

            <span
              class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3.4rem)] font-extrabold text-ateb-dark"
            >
              e
            </span>

            <img
              src="/Logo/Sankhya-logo.svg"
              alt="Sankhya"
              class="h-12 w-auto object-contain brightness-0 md:h-14 lg:h-16"
            />
          </span>
        </h1>

        <h3
          class="font-sora mx-auto max-w-[22ch] text-[clamp(1.25rem,2.8vw,2rem)] font-bold leading-[1.16] tracking-[-0.04em] text-ateb-earth lg:mx-0"
        >
          RM, Protheus, Fluig ou Sankhya
        </h3>

        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[680px] gap-4 lg:mx-0">
          <p
            class="text-[clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.16rem)] leading-[1.7] text-[rgba(77,72,55,0.84)]"
          >
            Sua empresa enfrenta retrabalho, controles manuais ou processos
            pouco integrados?
          </p>

          <p
            class="text-[clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.16rem)] leading-[1.7] text-[rgba(77,72,55,0.84)]"
          >
            Consultoria, automação e integração de sistemas ERP, com mais de 20
            anos de experiência para gerar mais controle, produtividade e
            organização.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex w-full flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 pt-2 lg:justify-start"
        >
          <a href={contactSectionUrl} class="ateb-button-accent">
            Solicitar diagnóstico estratégico
          </a>
        </div>

        <p
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[rgba(77,72,55,0.72)] lg:justify-start"
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true"
            ><svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 1000 700"
              class="h-4 w-6 rounded-sm shadow-sm"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <rect width="1000" height="700" fill="#009b3a"></rect>
              <polygon points="500,100 900,350 500,600 100,350" fill="#ffdf00"
              ></polygon>
              <circle cx="500" cy="350" r="140" fill="#002776"></circle>

              <path
                d="M360 330c40-25 90-40 140-40s100 15 140 40"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#fff"
                stroke-width="28"></path>
            </svg></span
          >
          Atendimento para empresas em todo o Brasil.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[560px] lg:mx-0 lg:ml-auto">
        <div
          class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-[12%] bottom-[6%] h-10 rounded-full bg-[rgba(29,18,10,0.16)] blur-[26px]"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class="pointer-events-none absolute right-[8%] top-[8%] h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-ateb-lime/20 blur-3xl"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>

        <img
          src="/images/background-hero.webp"
          alt="Imagem institucional da ATEB Soluções"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          class="relative mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-[820px] object-contain drop-shadow-[0_30px_50px_rgba(29,18,10,0.16)]"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
